criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria： ①Patients diagnosed as FIGO stage IA2、IB1、IIA1 cervical cancer ;
        ②Patients diagnosed as FIGO stage IB2、IIA2 cervical cancer, eligible for RH after
        neoadjuvant chemotherapy; ③Patients diagnosed as FIGO stage IIA endometrial carcinoma;
        ④Patients didn't have pelvic organ prolapse and urinary incontinence; ⑤Ability to hold
        Valsalva for dynamic MRI; ⑥Patients aged 20-70 years; ⑦Patients undergone RH surgery;
        ⑧Informed consent was signed.

        Exclusion Criteria：

        ①With MRI or urodynamic examination contraindication; ②Previously undergone POP or SUI
        surgery; ③BMI＞30 With serious postoperative complications.
